### Get all products (ดูสินค้าทั้งหมด)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v2/products

### --------------------------------------------------

### Create Product 1: Key-chain (สร้างพวงกุญแจ)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v2/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "P001",
  "productName": "Key-chain",
  "price": 99
}

### --------------------------------------------------

